><div><div><li><strong>Removable Enamel Interior for the Oven</strong></li></div><div>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Easy Clean Enamel Oven Interior\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1380.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Nanotechnologically Coated, All-Black Brass Burner</strong></li></div><div>An elegant Total Black finish complements the noble technical characteristics of brass, which are enhanced with a nanotechnological coating that guarantees easy cleaning.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Total Black Brass Burner With Non-Stick Nanotechnological Coating\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1447.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Cast-Iron Pan Supports for Your Cooktop (Hob)</strong></li></div><div>Cast iron pan supports are sturdy and long-lasting, so you can rest assured that your pots will be well-supported.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Cooktop (Hob) With Cast Iron Pan Supports\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1448.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Extremely Tailored Stovetops</strong></li></div><div>Crafted from AISI 304 steel with a 12/10 thickness, this versatile cooktop is available in a variety of configurations and can be used with gas or induction burners.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Highly Specialized Cooktops\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1449.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>As a Default, Two Gas Burners With A Maximum Power Of 20,000 BTU</strong></li></div><div>For every kind of cooking, the ideal supply and distribution of heat.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Dual Gas Burners With Power Up To 20000 BTU As Standard\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1474.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>A Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></li></div><div>With its TFT technology, the display guarantees excellent readability, showing every function with clear and immediate graphics. With a single touch of the large display, you can control all the functions of either the single oven or both ovens with a single device. One move and a glance controls the temperature, the timer, and the automatic cooking start and end programmer.</div><div><img alt=\\\"4.3 Inch Full Touch Display\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1475.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>A Statement of Ilve's Majesty</strong></li></div><div>Majestic is a daring and expert representation of the ideal range cooker; its rounded forms, forged in pure steel with painstakingly made details, will adorn your home with their beauty and functionality, which is a marriage of traditional Italian style and modern technology.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Ilve\\u2019S Majestic Statement\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1496.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>The Show-Stopping Range Cooker That Will Transform Your Kitchen</strong></li></div><div>When it comes to cooking, form follows function. ILVE puts its knowledge and expertise to work for you, providing solutions that combine high-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, ensuring the highest level of satisfaction at all times.</div><div><img alt=\\\"The Statement Range Cooker Which Makes Your Kitchen Unique\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/1497.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Party Pizza</strong></li></div><div>This oven is perfect for baking pizza, bread, focaccia, and other similar foods. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and it works in tandem with the other, less powerful heating elements to provide the ideal conditions for baking.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Pizza Function\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5160.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Fan Cooking with Multiple Moist Fans</strong></li></div><div>When cooking with multiple fans, this increases the moisture content.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Multiple Moist Fan Cooking\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5161.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Searing Food on a Grill While Covered</strong></li></div><div>Ideal for searing fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and even veggies quickly and thoroughly, as well as browning and roasting meat in general.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Grill Cooking With Closed Door\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5162.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Gentle Cooking from the Ground Up</strong></li></div><div>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Moist Cooking From Below\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5163.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Removing From Freeze</strong></li></div><div>It guarantees that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Defrosting\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5164.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></li></div><div>This steam-discharge cooker guarantees rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for foods that require a crunchy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, fish with a salt crust, etc.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Intensive Cooking\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5165.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Recipes from the Top</strong></li></div><div>Use it to brown and color a wide variety of foods; burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc. are some of the best candidates.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Cooking From Above\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5166.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></li></div><div>Pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, roast veal, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, etc. are all great candidates for this electric oven's classic function.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Static Normal Cooking\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5167.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Accelerated Learning</strong></li></div><div>With the fast oven preheating feature, it is possible to quickly get to the temperature you want, and then select the cooking mode that is most appropriate for the food. When set to a low temperature, it also functions as a rapid defroster.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Quick Start\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5168.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></li></div><div>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Moist Intensive Cooking\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5169.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Heavenly Homemade Recipes</strong></li></div><div>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Moist Cooking From Above\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5170.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Wet Static Regular Cooking</strong></li></div><div>Typical static cooking gets even more wet with this.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Moist Static Normal Cooking\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5171.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Cooking with Multiple Fans</strong></li></div><div>You can bake a variety of foods at once without worrying about their aromas blending\\u2014lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc.\\u2014and save both time and energy thanks to this feature.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Multiple Fan Cooking\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5172.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Searing on a Fan Grill</strong></li></div><div>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Fan Grill Cooking\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5173.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Making Food From Scratch</strong></li></div><div>Pastries (such as biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, etc.) are best cooked to perfection using this method.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Cooking From Below\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5174.jpg\\\"/></div></div><div><div><li><strong>Eco-Friendly Recipes</strong></li></div><div>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on, allowing you to cook with significantly less electricity consumption.</div><div><img alt=\\\"Eco Cooking\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/5175.jpg\\\"/></div></div> </div> </div></div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_specification\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" data-slug=\\\"specification\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_specification\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Specifications</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_specification\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_specification\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"> <ul><li><strong>Brand</strong>: ILVE</li><li><strong>Series</strong>: Majestic II</li><li><strong>Appliance Category</strong>: Range</li><br/><p><strong>Appearance</strong></p><li><strong>Color</strong>: Antique White</li><li><strong>Color Family</strong>: Antique White</li><li><strong>Design Style</strong>: Retro Style</li><li><strong>Trim</strong>: Burnished</li><br/><p><strong>Dimensions</strong></p><li><strong>Exterior Width</strong>: 40\\u2033</li><li><strong>Width</strong>: 39 3/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Depth</strong>: 29\\u2033</li><li><strong>Height</strong>: 38 3/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Depth with Door Opened at 90 Degrees</strong>: 42 7/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Product Weight (lbs)</strong>: 291</li><br/><p><strong>Fuel Type</strong></p><li><strong>Fuel Type</strong>: Electric</li><br/><p><strong>Style</strong></p><li><strong>Style</strong>: Freestanding</li><li><strong>Control Location</strong>: Front</li><br><p><strong>Capacity</strong></p><li><strong>Total Capacity (cu. ft.)</strong>: 3.82</li><li><strong>Number of Ovens</strong>: Double Oven</li><li><strong>Main Oven Capacity (cu. ft.)</strong>: 2.3</li><li><strong>Second Oven Capacity (cu. ft.)</strong>: 1.52</li><br><p><strong>Cooking Surface</strong></p><li><strong>Cooktop Configuration</strong>: Induction</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Type</strong>: Induction Element</li><li><strong>Number of Burners/Elements</strong>: 6</li><li><strong>Grill</strong>: No</li><li><strong>Griddle</strong>: No</li><li><strong>French Top</strong>: No</li><li><strong>Highest Element Output</strong>: 3200 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N1</strong>: 2500 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N2</strong>: 1800 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N3</strong>: 3200 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N4</strong>: 2500 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N5</strong>: 3200 Watts</li><li><strong>Burner/Element Output N6</strong>: 1800 Watts</li><br><p><strong>Oven</strong></p><li><strong>Oven Control Type</strong>: TFT Electronic Touchscreen</li><li><strong>Oven Door Type</strong>: Triple Glass Door</li><li><strong>Oven Cleaning Type</strong>: Easy Clean Enamel Cavities</li><li><strong>Main Oven Type</strong>: UOV 60 E3 TFT S</li><li><strong>Interior Width</strong>: 18 1/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Interior Height</strong>: 14 1/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Interior Depth</strong>: 16 1/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Second Oven Type</strong>: UOV 30 E3 TFT</li><li><strong>Secondary Interior Width</strong>: 10 7/8\\u2033</li><li><strong>Secondary Interior Height</strong>: 14\\u2033</li><li><strong>Secondary Interior Depth</strong>: 17 1/3\\u2033</li><br><p><strong>Technical Details</strong></p><li><strong>Voltage</strong>: 240</li><li><strong>Amps</strong>: 75.6</li><br/><p><strong>Certifications</strong></p><li><strong>Star-K Certified</strong>: Yes</li><br/><p><strong>Warranty</strong></p><li><strong>Warranty</strong>: 2 Year Parts and Labor