an><bdi><span>$</span>49.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+es4053008030006\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/ES4053008030006_p16237-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE ES4053008030006 Drip Pan For Standard Oven</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>130.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g00201\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G00201_p16239-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/01 Stainless Steel Bain-Marie (Double Boiler) for Hot Water Bath</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>382.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g00202\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G00202_p16240-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/02 Steam Cooker Basins</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>452.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g04001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G04001_p16241-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/040/01 Griddle Dome</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>245.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g4221208\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G4221208_p16378-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G4221208 Scroll Claw Leg (Sold by Individual Leg) (Chrome)</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>242.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Blue Grey\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Brass\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 40 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 6 Elements, Booster Function, Bridge Control, Residual Heat Indicator (Blue Grey / Copper / Triple Glass Door) - UMDI10NS3BGP\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMDI10NS3BGP\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_173279.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_173280.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_173281.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_1614.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_1615.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_1616.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_1617.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_1618.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_11270.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_11271.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_11272.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_11273.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BGP_p13668_33110.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"9990.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202236850\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>The Majestic 40-inch induction range is a perfect example of how traditional Italian design can coexist with modern technology. It has six efficient element zones, two total oven capacities of 2.3 and 1.52 cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><p>Availability: 90 - 120 days for pre-order</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>That show-stopping range cooker that will turn heads in your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>A freestanding showpiece with a style characterized by rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions, and technology originating from the realm of professional cooking, Majestic is a marriage of form and function, the perfect range cooker. Its beauty and functionality are expertly embodied.</p><p></p><p>The graceful curves and meticulously crafted details of majestic range cookers make them beautiful additions to any home.</p><p></p><p>Designed for your home's kitchen, these workhorses are available in a variety of colors (from 30 to 60 inches) and set-up options (from multiple options) and can be customized to RAL Classic shades upon request. They also feature fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Detector of residual heat</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Bridge management</li><li>Function that boosts</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Preventing harm to children</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Fire safety and prevention of overheating</li><li>Electronic temperature control with pinpoint accuracy</li><li>Drawer and door with a gentle closing mechanism</li><li>Fast start</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Innovations in Product Technology</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that guarantee the best satisfaction by combining top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Stove</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Dual-Platform Induction Cooktop</strong></p><p>Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) are a modern, practical, and safe method of cooking that combines cutting-edge technology with an elegant and modern aesthetic. Induction offers many benefits, such as safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Heat Residue Indicator</strong></p><p>The glass is hot, so be careful not to touch it or put anything on it; doing so could cause damage.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>Once the specified time has passed, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>With this function, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Capability</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Management</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>The induction cooktop (hob) cannot be turned on using the controls once this feature has been enabled and will remain so until disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Preventing Liquid Spills and Overheating</strong></p><p>A safety feature is installed to cut power in the event that the stovetop (hob) gets too hot or a spillage occurs.</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Oven Solutions</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Ovens: Massive Capacity and Peak Efficiency.</strong></p><p>With a 40-inch range that can hold up to 4 cubic feet of food, you'll have more than enough room for even the largest of dishes in any of our single or double combination ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electrical Temperature Regulation</strong></p><p>In contrast to traditional ovens, which experience temperature fluctuations, the electronic control keeps the oven temperature constant the whole time.</p><p></p><p><strong>A 4.3-inch Full-Touch Screen</strong></p><p>With TFT technology, the screen guarantees excellent legibility, showing quick and clear graphics for every function.</p><p></p><p><strong>The TFT display is user-friendly, comprehensive, and has a high resolution.</strong></p><p>All the controls for the oven, including temperature, timer, and automatic start/end programming, are conveniently located on the large display, so all you need is a single finger to operate either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously.</p><p></p><p><strong>Smooth-Closing Door System</strong></p><p>Shock absorbers installed in the door hinges allow for quieter, more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Soft-Closing Mechanism for the Warming Drawer</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Probe for Cooking</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection (Hot Food Preparation)</strong></p><p>If you want a crispy baked dish or a juicy roast, this system will remove the vapours from inside the cavity, giving you the option to cook it dry or wet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Using High Density Insulation and Tangential Cooling Ventilation</strong></p><p>Keeps the kitchen and its furniture from getting too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>The Ultimate Cleaning Solution: A Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Dishwasher Safe Enamel</strong></p><p>Grease is easier to remove since it does not adhere to the surface.</p><p></p><p><strong>Key Oven Responsibilities. UOV 60 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Warming up</li><li>Very intense cooking</li><li>A brief overview</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>From the ground up, cook</li><li>Cooking with moisture from below</li><li>Standard, unchanging cooking</li><li>Normal static cooking that is moist</li><li>Using multiple fan cooking</li><li>Several wet fan ovens</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Utility of Secondary Ovens. 30 E3 TFT UOV</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>An Underground Kitchen</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Party Pizza</strong></p><p>This oven is perfect for baking pizza, bread, focaccia, and other similar foods. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and it works in tandem with the other, less powerful heating elements to provide the ideal conditions for baking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>It guarantees that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>For foods that require a crispy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc., this steam-discharge method guarantees rapid and intense cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Easy Beginning</strong></p><p>Quickly get to the temperature you want with the preheating function, then select the cooking mode that works best for your dish. When set to low, it also defrosts quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>Many foods, including sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc., can be cooked quickly and thoroughly with this function, which also significantly reduces energy consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling under Covered Spaces</strong></p><p>Ideal for searing fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and even veggies quickly and thoroughly, as well as browning and roasting meat in general.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Cooking</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc., all benefit from browning and the finishing touch of color that this function provides.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>How to Cook Everything from Scratch</strong></p><p>For pastries (biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking the cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>In-Depth Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy, Regular, Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>Typical static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Multiple Fans</strong></p><p>You can bake a variety of foods at once without worrying about their aromas blending\\u2014lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc.\\u2014and save both time and energy thanks to this feature.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>When cooking with multiple fans, this increases the moisture content.</p><p></p><p><strong>Sustainability in the Kitchen</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Proposition 65 in California\\u2014</strong></p><p>Caution: Danger to Health and Fertility</p><p><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov for more information. C</a></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/wKi6ZYNcCxY.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/re1Uo4qdmcc.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/4JuPNm3uQqU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> </div></div><br/><br/><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><