1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE ES4053008030006 Drip Pan For Standard Oven</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>130.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g00201\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G00201_p16239-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/01 Stainless Steel Bain-Marie (Double Boiler) for Hot Water Bath</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>382.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g00202\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G00202_p16240-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/02 Steam Cooker Basins</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>452.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g04001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G04001_p16241-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/040/01 Griddle Dome</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>245.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g4221208\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G4221208_p16378-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G4221208 Scroll Claw Leg (Sold by Individual Leg) (Chrome)</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>242.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Glossy Black\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Chrome\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 40 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 6 Elements, Booster Function, Bridge Control, Residual Heat Indicator (Glossy Black / Brass / Triple Glass Door) - UMDI10NS3BKG\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMDI10NS3BKG\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694_173288.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694_173289.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694_173290.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694_11282.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694_11283.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694_11284.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694_11285.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3BKG_p13694_33113.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"9990.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202193436\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>The 40-inch Majestic induction range is a perfect example of how traditional Italian design can coexist with modern technology. It has six efficient element zones, two total oven capacities of 2.3 and 1.52 cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that effortlessly integrates into any space while commanding attention with its striking combination of form and function. Its design draws inspiration from the world of professional cooking and features rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, and solutions and technologies that are both practical and aesthetically pleasing.</p><p></p><p>Majestic range cookers are works of art in and of themselves, but they also serve as functional kitchen appliances because of the meticulous craftsmanship that goes into their curved, all-steel designs.</p><p></p><p>Designed for your home's kitchen, these workhorses are available in a variety of colors (from 30 to 60 inches) and set-up options (from multiple options) and can be customized to RAL Classic shades upon request. They also feature fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Evidence of residual heat</li><li>Timer with built-in stop function</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Enhancement feature</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Ensuring the safety of children</li><li>Widescreen 4.3-inch</li><li>Safety from overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Electronic temperature control with pinpoint accuracy</li><li>Cabinet and door soft-closing mechanism</li><li>Getting started with little</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Advancements in Product Technologies</strong></p><p></p><p>When it comes to cooking, form follows function. ILVE puts its knowledge and expertise to work for you, providing solutions that combine high-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, ensuring the highest level of satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Range</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Dual-Platform Induction Cooktop</strong></p><p>With their modern technology and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) make cooking a breeze. Induction offers many benefits, such as safe cooking, reduced energy consumption, safety, adjustable temperature control, and quick cooking times, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measurement of Persistent Heat</strong></p><p>The glass is hot, so be careful not to touch it or put anything on it; doing so could cause damage.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>Activates the active zone until the timer goes off.</p><p></p><p><strong>Managing Bridges</strong></p><p>If your induction cooktop (hob) has this capability, you can treat two adjacent zones as one and use a single command to control them both.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Puts the induction cooktop's (hob's) full power into the predetermined area, allowing you to boil and cook more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>The induction cooktop (hob) cannot be turned on using the controls once this feature has been enabled and will remain so until disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Limiting Heat and Preventing Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>An automatic shutoff mechanism activates in the event of a liquid spill or overheating of the cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Oven Solutions</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Ovens: Massive Capacity and Peak Efficiency.</strong></p><p>Our 40-inch range offers an oven capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you'll have plenty of room for even the largest of dishes with any combination oven, single or double.</p><p></p><p><strong>Electronic Temperature Control with High Precision</strong></p><p>The oven's temperature stays consistent throughout thanks to the electronic control, unlike with traditional ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>4.3\\\" Touch Screen Display</strong></p><p>The display's TFT technology guarantees excellent readability by showing quick and clear graphics for each function.</p><p></p><p><strong>Our TFT display is designed to be user-friendly, comprehensive, and high resolution.</strong></p><p>All the controls for the oven, including temperature, timer, and automatic start/end programming, are conveniently located on the large display, so all you need is a single finger to operate either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously.</p><p></p><p><strong>Smooth-Closing Door System</strong></p><p>A shock absorber is integrated into the door hinges, allowing for a quieter and more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cabinet with Warming Drawer and Soft-Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Food Preparation Tester</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection (Hot Food Preparation)</strong></p><p>To get a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast, this system removes the vapours from inside the cavity, giving you the option to cook it dry or wet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Range of temperatures: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Using High Density Insulation and Tangential Cooling Ventilation</strong></p><p>Ensures that the kitchen and its adjacent furniture do not become too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>The Ultimate Cleaning Solution: A Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>The electric heating element of the grill can be lowered for easier cleaning of the top part of the cavity, thanks to the articulated support.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rinse-Free Enamel</strong></p><p>Grease is easier to remove since it does not adhere to the surface.</p><p></p><p><strong>Essential Oven Operations. UOV 60 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>The pizza party</li><li>Removing From Freeze</li><li>Prolonged cooking</li><li>Getting started with little</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Steaming food cooked in the air</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Cooking with moisture from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Standard static cooking with moisture</li><li>Numerous fan-assisted cooking methods</li><li>Various wet fan cooking methods</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Additional Oven Purposes. UOV 30 E3 TFT</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Standard, unchanging cooking</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><hr/><p></p><p><strong>A Pizza Party</strong></p><p>The lower heating element, in conjunction with the other, less powerful heating elements, produces the ideal temperature and baking conditions for pizza, bread, and focaccia.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>Ensures that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thorough Preparation</strong></p><p>This steam-discharge cooker guarantees rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for foods that require a crunchy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, fish with a salt crust, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Easy Beginning</strong></p><p>Find the ideal cooking mode for your food with the help of the fast preheating function; when set to a low temperature, it also functions as a rapid defroster.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>For moist cooking, such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, chicken cacciatore, etc., it ensures rapid and intense cooking with steam block.</p><p></p><p><strong>Searing on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>Many foods, including sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc., can be cooked quickly and thoroughly with this function, which also significantly reduces energy consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Open-Top Grilling with a Closed Door</strong></p><p>Functions such as quick and deep grilling, browning, roasting, and cooking fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and vegetables are highly recommended.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, and many more foods benefit from this function's browning and color-enhancing capabilities.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>From the Ground Up: A Culinary Adventure</strong></p><p>With the exception of leavened desserts (biscuits, meringues, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking pastries.</p><p></p><p><strong>In-Depth Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>If you want to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture, this is the way to go.</p><p></p><p><strong>Standard, Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Cooking with Moist Static</strong></p><p>This makes traditional static cooking even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>This increases the amount of moisture in a standard multi-fan oven.</p><p></p><p><strong>Natural Food Preparation</strong></p><p>Slow roasting foods, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, and delicate pastries, necessitate longer cooking times when using the ECO function, which significantly reduces power consumption. However, this cooking cycle is not meant for foods that are frozen.</p><p></p><p><strong>Proposition 65 in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Possible Cancer and Harm to Fertility</p><p><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov