6239-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/01 Stainless Steel Bain-Marie (Double Boiler) for Hot Water Bath</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>382.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g00202\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G00202_p16240-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/002/02 Steam Cooker Basins</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>452.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g04001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G04001_p16241-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G/040/01 Griddle Dome</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>245.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+g4221208\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G4221208_p16378-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G4221208 Scroll Claw Leg (Sold by Individual Leg) (Chrome)</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>242.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Graphite Matte\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Chrome\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 40 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 6 Elements, Booster Function, Bridge Control, Residual Heat Indicator (Graphite Matte / Brass / Triple Glass Door) - UMDI10NS3MGG\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMDI10NS3MGG\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686_173336.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686_173337.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686_173338.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686_59510.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686_11346.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686_11347.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686_11348.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686_11349.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3MGG_p13686_33129.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"9990.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202193382\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>The 40-inch Majestic induction range is a perfect example of how traditional Italian design can coexist with modern technology. It has six efficient element zones, two total oven capacities of 2.3 and 1.52 cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><p>Currently Available: Yes</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>That show-stopping range cooker that will turn heads in your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic, a freestanding statement-piece with a style that incorporates rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions, and technologies derived from the world of professional cooking, is a beautiful and functional fusion of form and function. It effortlessly blends into any setting while still taking center stage.</p><p></p><p>The sculpted, meticulously detailed forms of majestic range cookers, crafted from pure steel, make them eye-catching kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative accents.</p><p></p><p>They are masterpieces of craftsmanship, crafted for your home's kitchen. They come in a variety of colors, including RAL Classic shades upon request, and are complemented by fine metallic finishes. They are available in a wide range of sizes, from 30 to 60 inches, and provide multiple options for installation.</p><p></p><ul><li>Detector of residual heat</li><li>Timer that stops automatically</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Enhancement feature</li><li>Handles for sliding</li><li>Protecting children</li><li>Widescreen 4.3-inch</li><li>Fire safety and prevention of overheating</li><li>Electronic temperature control with pinpoint accuracy</li><li>Drawer and door with a gentle closing mechanism</li><li>Getting started quickly</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Advancements in Product Technologies</strong></p><p></p><p>Although aesthetics are important, having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE offers solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, combining these factors to guarantee the best satisfaction.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies related to stovetops</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Induction Range (Oven)</strong></p><p>Using cutting-edge technology in a stylish and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) expedite the cooking process while minimizing the risk of burns and other food hazards. Induction also helps with cleaning, energy savings, safety, temperature control, and cooking speed, all of which are important when it comes to preparing meals and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Calculator for Remaining Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>At the end of the specified time, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>If your induction cooktop (hob) has this capability, you can treat two adjacent zones as one and use a single command to control them both.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>By simply gliding your finger from side to side, you can adjust the operating temperature, for instance, thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Protecting Children</strong></p><p>After you enable this feature, you can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><p><strong>Preventing Liquid Spills and Overheating</strong></p><p>A safety device will trip and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Ovens: Massive Capacity and Peak Efficiency.</strong></p><p>Our 40-inch range offers an oven capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you'll have plenty of room for even the largest of dishes with any combination oven, single or double.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>In contrast to traditional ovens, which experience temperature fluctuations, the electronic control keeps the oven temperature constant the whole time.</p><p></p><p><strong>Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></p><p>Displaying every function with clear and immediate graphics, the display guarantees superior readability thanks to TFT technology.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>All the controls for the oven, including temperature, timer, and automatic start/end programming, are conveniently located on the large display, so all you need is a single finger to operate either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously.</p><p></p><p><strong>Door with a System for Soft Closing</strong></p><p>A shock absorber is integrated into the door hinges, allowing for a quieter and more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Drawer Heater with Soft-Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Food Preparation Assessment Tool</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection (Hot Food Preparation)</strong></p><p>You can achieve a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast thanks to this system, which removes the vapors from inside the cavity, allowing you to choose a drier or more moist cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Wide temperature range (85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit)</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Inspiring Cooling Air and Dense Insulation</strong></p><p>Ensures that the kitchen and its adjacent furniture do not become too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grill Coil that Folds for Easy Cleaning</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rinse-Free Enamel</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Main Duties of the Oven. UOV 60 E3 TFT Solar</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing from Freeze</li><li>Prolonged cooking</li><li>Fast start</li><li>Extremely moist cooking</li><li>The cooking method of the fan grill</li><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Steaming food cooked in the air</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Cooking with moisture from below</li><li>Standard, unchanging cooking</li><li>Standard static cooking with moisture</li><li>Using a number of fans to cook</li><li>Various wet fan cooking methods</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Utility of Secondary Ovens. 30 E3 TFT UOV</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Recipes viewed from above</li><li>Starting with the base</li><li>Standard, unchanging cooking</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><hr/><p></p><p><strong>A Pizza Party</strong></p><p>The lower heating element, in conjunction with the other, less powerful heating elements, produces the ideal temperature and baking conditions for pizza, bread, and focaccia.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing From Freeze</strong></p><p>It guarantees that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>This steam-discharge cooker guarantees rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for foods that require a crunchy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, fish with a salt crust, etc.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rapid Start</strong></p><p>With the fast preheating function, you can quickly get to the temperature you want, and then select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also double as a rapid defroster.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Searing on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling in a Room with No Doors Open</strong></p><p>Ideal for searing fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and even veggies quickly and thoroughly, as well as browning and roasting meat in general.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>This function is perfect for browning and finishing a wide variety of foods; burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc. all benefit from it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Lessons in Home Cooking</strong></p><p>For pastries (biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking the cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>In-Depth Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Wet Static Regular Cooking</strong></p><p>Typical static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>You can bake a variety of foods at once without worrying about their aromas blending\\u2014lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc.\\u2014and save both time and energy thanks to this feature.</p><p></p><p><strong>Fan Cooking with Multiple Moist Fans</strong></p><p>This makes regular cooking with multiple fans even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Low-Cost Ethical Cuisine</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>The 65th Proposition in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Possible Cancer and Harm to Fertility</p><p><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov as a governmen