dn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Graphite Matte\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Copper\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 40 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 6 Elements, Booster Function, Bridge Control, Residual Heat Indicator (RAL / Burnished / Triple Glass Door) - UMDI10NS3RAB\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMDI10NS3RAB\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728_173342.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728_173343.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728_173344.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728_11358.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728_11359.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728_11360.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728_11361.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728_33183.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAB_p13728_33131.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"12790.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202255547\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>Featuring a 4.3-inch full-touch oven control display, an easy-clean enamel oven cavity, a total oven capacity of 2.3 + 1.52 cu. ft., and a classic Italian design aesthetic, the Majestic 40-inch induction range is a technological marvel.</p><p>Availability: 90 - 120 days for pre-order</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>The show-stopping range cooker that will turn heads in your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>With its rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions, and technologies derived from the world of professional cooking, Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that effortlessly blends into any setting while still commanding attention. It is a masterful embodiment of the ultimate range cooker, combining form and function.</p><p></p><p>The sculpted, meticulously detailed forms of majestic range cookers, crafted from pure steel, make them eye-catching kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative accents.</p><p></p><p>Designed for your home's kitchen, these workhorses are available in a variety of colors (from 30 to 60 inches) and set-up options (from multiple options) and can be customized to RAL Classic shades upon request. They also feature fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Indictor for residual heat</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Manage bridges</li><li>Function that boosts</li><li>Handles for sliding</li><li>Ensuring the safety of children</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Safety from overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Drawer and door with a gentle closing mechanism</li><li>A brief introduction</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Innovations in Product Technology</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that guarantee the best satisfaction by combining top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies related to stovetops</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Dual-Platform Induction Cooktop</strong></p><p>With their modern technology and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) make cooking a breeze. Induction offers many benefits, such as safe cooking, reduced energy consumption, safety, adjustable temperature control, and quick cooking times, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Heat Residue Indicator</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>Once the specified time has passed, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Managing Bridges</strong></p><p>With this function, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Capability</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Management</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>You can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob) once this feature is enabled; it remains disabled until you disable it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Protecting Against Overheating and Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>A safety mechanism will activate and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Oven Solutions</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Massive and Efficient Ovens.</strong></p><p>We have a 40-inch range with a capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you can choose between a single or double combination oven that will give you plenty of room, even for big dishes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>The oven's temperature stays consistent throughout thanks to the electronic control, unlike with traditional ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>4.3\\\" Touch Screen Display</strong></p><p>The display guarantees excellent readability with TFT technology, showing every function with clear and immediate graphics.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>With a single touch of the big screen, you can control all the features of either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously. You can set the temperature, set the timer, and program the ovens to start and stop cooking automatically.</p><p></p><p><strong>Comfortably Closing Door System</strong></p><p>With the shock absorber installed in the door hinges, closing the door is a more gradual and noiseless process.</p><p></p><p><strong>Drawer Heater with Soft-Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Food Preparation Tester</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection for Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>You can achieve a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast thanks to this system, which removes the vapors from inside the cavity, allowing you to choose a drier or more moist cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>Whether your recipe calls for proofing, cooking, roasting, or low temperature, an ILVE oven can handle it all with ease and produce flawless results.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Inspiring Cooling Air and Dense Insulation</strong></p><p>Keeps kitchen and oven furniture from getting too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Collapsible Grill Coil for Thorough Cleaning</strong></p><p>The grill's electric heating element can be lowered for easier cleaning of the top part of the cavity, all because of the articulated support.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rinse-Free Enamel</strong></p><p>Grease is easier to remove since it does not adhere to the surface.</p><p></p><p><strong>Essential Baking Processes. UOV 60 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing From Freeze</li><li>Prolonged cooking</li><li>Fast start</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>An Underground Kitchen</li><li>Preparing moist food from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Static, moist, typical cooking</li><li>Using a number of fans to cook</li><li>A variety of moist fan ovens</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Additional Oven Purposes. UOV 30 E3 TFT</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Basic, unchanging cooking</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><hr/><p></p><p><strong>A Pizza Party</strong></p><p>This oven is perfect for baking pizza, bread, focaccia, and other similar foods. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and it works in tandem with the other, less powerful heating elements to provide the ideal conditions for baking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>It guarantees that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>For foods that require a crispy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc., this steam-discharge method guarantees rapid and intense cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rapid Start</strong></p><p>With the fast preheating function, you can quickly get to the temperature you want, and then select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. What's more, when set to a low temperature, it can also function as rapid defrosting.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Searing on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>Many foods, including sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc., can be cooked quickly and thoroughly with this function, which also significantly reduces energy consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Charcoal Grilling with a Closed Door</strong></p><p>Use this function for browning and roasting meat, fish, vegetables, fillets, Florentine steak, and other types of meat quickly and thoroughly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Cooking</strong></p><p>Burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc., all benefit from browning and the finishing touch of color that this function provides.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Perfect for turning foods a golden brown while still keeping them tender, it also gives a variety of dishes their final color.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes Performed from the Ground Up</strong></p><p>For pastries (biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking the cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes Made from Scratch</strong></p><p>If you want to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture, this is the way to go.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Damp Static Regular Cooking</strong></p><p>Typical static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Multiple Fans</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>When cooking with multiple fans, this increases the moisture content.</p><p></p><p><strong>Creating a Sustainable Diet</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Equal Rights Amendment in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Danger to Health and Fertility</p><p><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov for more information.</a></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/wKi6ZYNcCxY.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/re1Uo4qdmcc.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/sh