ntent/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAG_p13726_33185.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10NS3RAG_p13726_33133.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"12790.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202255561\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>Featuring a 4.3-inch full-touch oven control display, an easy-clean enamel oven cavity, a total oven capacity of 2.3 + 1.52 cu. ft., and a classic Italian design aesthetic, the Majestic 40-inch induction range is a technological marvel.</p><p>Availability: 90 - 120 days for pre-order</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>The show-stopping range cooker that will turn your kitchen into a showpiece.</p><p></p><p>With its rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions, and technologies derived from the world of professional cooking, Majestic is a freestanding statement-piece that effortlessly blends into any setting while still commanding attention. It is a masterful embodiment of the ultimate range cooker, combining form and function.</p><p></p><p>Majestic range cookers are works of art in and of themselves, but they also serve as functional kitchen appliances because of the meticulous craftsmanship that goes into their curved, all-steel designs.</p><p></p><p>Designed for your home's kitchen, these workhorses are available in a variety of colors (from 30 to 60 inches) and set-up options (from multiple options) and can be customized to RAL Classic shades upon request. They also feature fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Indictor for residual heat</li><li>Scheduler with built-in timeout</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Enhancement feature</li><li>Handles for sliding</li><li>Protecting children</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Fire safety and prevention of overheating</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Drawer and door with a gentle closing mechanism</li><li>Fast start</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Advancements in Product Technologies</strong></p><p></p><p>When it comes to cooking, form follows function. ILVE puts its knowledge and expertise to work for you, providing solutions that combine high-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, ensuring the highest level of satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Range</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Dual-Platform Induction Cooktop</strong></p><p>Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) are a modern, practical, and safe method of cooking that combines cutting-edge technology with an elegant and modern aesthetic. Induction offers many benefits, such as safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed, all of which make it easier to prepare dishes and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measurement of Persistent Heat</strong></p><p>Wear protective gloves and avoid touching or setting anything delicate on the glass because it is hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Automatically Stops the Timer</strong></p><p>Once the specified time has passed, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Bridge Management</strong></p><p>With this function, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhancement Role</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Handles</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>The induction cooktop (hob) cannot be turned on using the controls once this feature has been enabled and will remain so until disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Limiting Heat and Preventing Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>A safety mechanism will activate and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Impressive Size and Power: The Ovens.</strong></p><p>Our 40-inch range offers an oven capacity of up to 4 cubic feet, so you'll have plenty of room for even the largest of dishes with any combination oven, single or double.</p><p></p><p><strong>Electronic Temperature Control with Utmost Precision</strong></p><p>In contrast to traditional ovens, which experience temperature fluctuations, the electronic control keeps the oven temperature constant the whole time.</p><p></p><p><strong>Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></p><p>With TFT technology, the screen guarantees excellent legibility, showing quick and clear graphics for every function.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>All the controls for the oven, including temperature, timer, and automatic start/end programming, are conveniently located on the large display, so all you need is a single finger to operate either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously.</p><p></p><p><strong>Comfortably Closing Door System</strong></p><p>Shock absorbers installed in the door hinges allow for quieter, more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cabinet with Warming Drawer and Soft-Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Cooking Probe</strong></p><p>A must-have tool for taking internal temperatures, such as those of meat slices.</p><p></p><p><strong>Discharge of Steam for Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>You can achieve a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast thanks to this system, which removes the vapors from inside the cavity, allowing you to choose a drier or more moist cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Humidity range of 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>You can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes in an ILVE oven, whether you're proofing, cooking, roasting, or using low heat.</p><p></p><p><strong>Airflow for Tangential Cooling and High-Density Insulation</strong></p><p>Shields kitchen and oven-related furniture from dangerously high temperatures.</p><p></p><p><strong>The Ultimate Cleaning Solution: A Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>You can clean the top part of the cavity more easily thanks to the articulated support, which allows you to lower the electric heating element of the grill.</p><p></p><p><strong>Clean Enamel with Ease</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Key Oven Responsibilities. UOV 60 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>The pizza party</li><li>Removing From Freeze</li><li>Prolonged cooking</li><li>Fast start</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Steaming food cooked in the air</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Using moisture from below</li><li>Plain old cooking</li><li>Damp static regular cooking</li><li>Using multiple fan cooking options</li><li>Several wet fan ovens</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Oven Performance with UOV 30 E3 TFT</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Cooking on the grill with the door closed</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>An Underground Kitchen</li><li>Standard, unchanging cooking</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Party Pizza</strong></p><p>This oven is perfect for baking pizza, bread, focaccia, and other similar foods. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and it works in tandem with the other, less powerful heating elements to provide the ideal conditions for baking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing From Freeze</strong></p><p>Guarantees rapid thawing of any and all frozen foods, bringing them to room temperature without changing their flavor or texture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thorough Cooking</strong></p><p>For foods that require a crispy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc., this steam-discharge method guarantees rapid and intense cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Rapid Start</strong></p><p>Quick preheating gets the oven to the temperature you want it to be in no time at all, and then you can select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also defrost food quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Cooking with Moisture</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling with a Fan</strong></p><p>Many foods, including sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc., can be cooked quickly and thoroughly with this function, which also significantly reduces energy consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Methods for Grilling with a Closed Door</strong></p><p>Functions such as quick and deep grilling, browning, roasting, and cooking fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and vegetables are highly recommended.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>This function is perfect for browning and finishing a wide variety of foods; burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc. all benefit from it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heavenly, Moist Recipes</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Making Food from the Ground Up</strong></p><p>For pastries (biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking the cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>Healthy Recipes Made from Scratch</strong></p><p>In order to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture, this is the best way to do it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></p><p>This is the standard setting for electric ovens and is great for browning pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, roast veal, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and many more foods.</p><p></p><p><strong>Wet Static Regular Cooking</strong></p><p>Standard static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>This increases the amount of moisture in a standard multi-fan oven.</p><p></p><p><strong>eco-friendly food preparation</strong></p><p>With the ECO function, cooking times adapt to slow roasting, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, delicate pastries, and so on. This cooking cycle is not meant for frozen foods, but it does allow for significant savings on electricity consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Measure 65 in California</strong></p><p>Caution: Possible Cancer and Harm to Fertility</p><p><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov for more information.</a></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">Sorry, but the video tag isn't compatible with your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\