ding=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G4221208_p16378-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G4221208 Scroll Claw Leg (Sold by Individual Leg) (Chrome)</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>242.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"Burgundy\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Copper\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Solid Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 40 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 6 Elements, Booster Function, Bridge Control, Residual Heat Indicator (Emerald Green / Burnished / Solid Door) - UMDI10QNS3EGB\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMDI10QNS3EGB\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681_173438.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681_173439.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681_173440.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681_11466.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681_11467.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681_11468.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681_11469.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3EGB_p13681_33159.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"10690.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202220415\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>The 40-inch Majestic induction range is a perfect example of how traditional Italian design can coexist with modern technology. It has six efficient element zones, two total oven capacities of 2.3 and 1.52 cubic feet, a 4.3-inch full-touch control display, and an enamel oven cavity that is easy to clean.</p><p>Order now for delivery in 90 to 120 days!</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>A freestanding showpiece with a style characterized by rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions, and technology originating from the realm of professional cooking, Majestic is a marriage of form and function, the perfect range cooker. Its beauty and functionality are expertly embodied.</p><p></p><p>The sculpted, meticulously detailed forms of majestic range cookers, crafted from pure steel, make them eye-catching kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative accents.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Detector of remaining heat</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Enhancement feature</li><li>Controls that slide</li><li>Ensuring children's safety</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Safeguarding against overheating and liquid spills</li><li>Accurate electronic regulation of temperature</li><li>Cabinet and door soft-closing mechanism</li><li>A brief introduction</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Innovations in Product Technology</strong></p><p></p><p>Having the best technologies available to cook well and with pleasure is just as important as having attractive designs. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you by providing solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, ensuring the best satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Range</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Induction Range (Oven)</strong></p><p>With their modern technology and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) make cooking a breeze. Induction facilitates the preparation of dishes and recipes with its many benefits, including safety, ease of cleaning, energy savings, and versatile temperature control and cooking speed.</p><p></p><p><strong>Detector of Remaining Heat</strong></p><p>The glass is hot, so be careful not to touch it or put anything on it; doing so could cause damage.</p><p></p><p><strong>Stop-Starting Timer</strong></p><p>Once the specified time has passed, the active zone is disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>With this function, induction cooktops (hobs) allow you to control two adjacent zones with one command, as if they were one big zone.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Capability</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Management</strong></p><p>For instance, you can adjust the operating temperature simply by gliding your finger from right to left or left to right thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Ensuring Safety for Children</strong></p><p>The induction cooktop (hob) cannot be turned on using the controls once this feature has been enabled and will remain so until disabled.</p><p></p><p><strong>Prevention of Overheating and Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>A safety feature will activate and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>The Oven Guys</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Massive and Efficient Ovens.</strong></p><p>With a 40-inch range that can hold up to 4 cubic feet of food, you'll have more than enough room for even the largest of dishes in any of our single or double combination ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accurate Electronic Regulation of Temperature</strong></p><p>Unlike with traditional ovens, the temperature of the oven will stay consistent thanks to the electronic control.</p><p></p><p><strong>Full-Screen 4.3-Inch Display</strong></p><p>The display's TFT technology guarantees excellent readability by showing quick and clear graphics for each function.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>All the controls for the oven, including temperature, timer, and automatic start/end programming, are conveniently located on the large display, so all you need is a single finger to operate either the single oven or both ovens simultaneously.</p><p></p><p><strong>Doors with a Gentle Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p>With the shock absorber installed in the door hinges, closing the door is a more gradual and noiseless process.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cabinet with Warming Drawer and Soft-Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Probe for Cooking</strong></p><p>The tool you need to check the internal temperature of meat, among other things.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection for Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>To get a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast, this system removes the vapours from inside the cavity, giving you the option to cook it dry or wet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Humidity range of 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>With an ILVE oven, you can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes, whether you're roasting, cooking, or proofing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Using High Density Insulation and Tangential Cooling Ventilation</strong></p><p>Shields kitchen and oven-related furniture from dangerously high temperatures.</p><p></p><p><strong>Effortless Cleaning with the Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>The electric heating element of the grill can be lowered for easier cleaning of the top part of the cavity, thanks to the articulated support.</p><p></p><p><strong>Clean Enamel with Ease</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Essential Oven Operations. UOV 60 E3 TFT STM</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>The pizza party</li><li>Removing from Freeze</li><li>Cooking to extremes</li><li>Fast start</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Cooking with moisture from above</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Preparing moist food from below</li><li>Constant, everyday cooking</li><li>Standard static cooking with moisture</li><li>Numerous fan-assisted cooking methods</li><li>Various wet fan cooking methods</li><li>Green food preparation</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Utility of Secondary Ovens. 30 E3 TFT UOV</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Making food from on high</li><li>Starting with the base</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Pizza Party</strong></p><p>The lower heating element, in conjunction with the other, less powerful heating elements, produces the ideal temperature and baking conditions for pizza, bread, and focaccia.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>Ensures that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking to the Extremes</strong></p><p>For foods that require a crispy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc., this steam-discharge method guarantees rapid and intense cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accelerated Learning</strong></p><p>With the fast preheating function, you can quickly get to the temperature you want, and then select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. What's more, when set to a low temperature, it can also function as rapid defrosting.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extremely Wet Cooking</strong></p><p>The steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking, making it ideal for moist foods like salt cod, stewed rabbit, braised meat, chicken cacciatore, and braised meats.</p><p></p><p><strong>Searing on a Fan Grill</strong></p><p>Many foods, including sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc., can be cooked quickly and thoroughly with this function, which also significantly reduces energy consumption.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling under Covered Spaces</strong></p><p>Functions such as quick and deep grilling, browning, roasting, and cooking fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and vegetables are highly recommended.</p><p></p><p><strong>Recipes from the Sky</strong></p><p>This function is perfect for browning and finishing a wide variety of foods; burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc. all benefit from it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Excellent for browning and finishing the color of a wide variety of foods without mushiness.</p><p></p><p><strong>Beginning with the Basics in the Kitchen</strong></p><p>With the exception of leavened desserts (biscuits, meringues, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking pastries.</p><p></p><p><strong>In-Depth Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>This is the best way to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture.</p><p></p><p><strong>Regular, Unchanging Cooking</strong></p><p>Pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, roast veal, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, etc. are all great candidates for this electric oven's classic function.</p><p></p><p><strong>Normal Cooking with Moist Static</strong></p><p>This makes traditional static cooking even more moist.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Multiple Fans</strong></p><p>Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can all be baked at the same time without blending aromas thanks to this feature, which also helps to save power and time.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Multiple Moist Fans</strong></p><p>This increases the amount of moisture in a standard multi-fan oven.</p><p></p><p><strong>Sustainable Food Preparation\\n</strong></p><p>Slow roasting foods, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, and delicate pastries, necessitate longer cooking times when using the ECO function, which significantly reduces power consumption. However, this cooking cycle is not meant for foods that are frozen.</p><p></p><p><strong>Proposition 65 in California\\u2014</strong></p><p>Caution: Danger to Health and Fertility</p><p><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov for more information.</a></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">Sorry, but the video tag isn't compatible with your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/wKi6ZYNcCxY.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"