221208\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/G4221208_p16378-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE G4221208 Scroll Claw Leg (Sold by Individual Leg) (Chrome)</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>242.00</bdi></span></a></div><div><a href=\\\"/search?q=ilve+kgset001\\\"><div><img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/KGSET001_p20076.jpg\\\" width=\\\"115\\\"/></div><div>ILVE KGSET001 Total Extension Glide Racks</div><span><bdi><span>$</span>168.00</bdi></span></a></div></div> </div> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"RAL\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Burnished\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Solid Door\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"ILVE - 40 inch Majestic II Induction Range with 6 Elements, Booster Function, Bridge Control, Residual Heat Indicator (RAL / Chrome / Solid Door) - UMDI10QNS3RAC\", \"Variant SKU\": \"UMDI10QNS3RAC\", \"Variant Image\": \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731.jpg\", \"Variant All Images\": [\"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731_173515.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731_173516.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731_173517.png\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731_11526.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731_11527.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731_11528.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731_11529.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731_33188.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/UMDI10QNS3RAC_p13731_33172.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"13490.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202255592\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \" <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><p>Featuring a 4.3-inch full-touch oven control display, an easy-clean enamel oven cavity, a total oven capacity of 2.3 + 1.52 cu. ft., and a classic Italian design aesthetic, the Majestic 40-inch induction range is a technological marvel.</p><p>Order now for delivery in 90 to 120 days!</p><div><p><strong>Majestic</strong></p><p>This show-stopping range cooker will be the focal point of your kitchen.</p><p></p><p>Majestic, a freestanding statement-piece with a style that incorporates rounded lines, crafted details, fine finishes, solutions, and technologies derived from the world of professional cooking, is a beautiful and functional fusion of form and function. It effortlessly blends into any setting while still taking center stage.</p><p></p><p>The sculpted, meticulously detailed forms of majestic range cookers, crafted from pure steel, make them eye-catching kitchen appliances that also serve as decorative accents.</p><p></p><p>These are the real deal, hand-picked gems of professional design for your home kitchen. They come in a variety of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and offer a plethora of set-up options, as well as RAL Classic shades upon request and fine metallic finishes.</p><p></p><ul><li>Heat indicator with residual</li><li>Automatically stops the timer</li><li>Control of bridges</li><li>Booster role</li><li>Handles for sliding</li><li>Protecting children</li><li>Retina 4.3-inch touchscreen</li><li>Preventing overheating and liquid spillage</li><li>Electronic temperature control with pinpoint accuracy</li><li>Cabinet and door soft-closing mechanism</li><li>Getting started with little</li></ul><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Technology for Products</strong></p><p></p><p>Not only is aesthetics important, but having the best technologies available is essential for cooking well and enjoying oneself. ILVE puts its research and experience to work for you, providing solutions that combine top-level performance with maximum simplicity, safety, and user-friendliness, guaranteeing the best satisfaction at all times.</p><p></p><p><strong>Technologies for the Kitchen Range</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Dual-Platform Induction Cooktop</strong></p><p>Using cutting-edge technology in a stylish and elegant design, Majestic induction cooktops (hobs) expedite the cooking process while minimizing the risk of burns and other food hazards. Induction also helps with cleaning, energy savings, safety, temperature control, and cooking speed, all of which are important when it comes to preparing meals and recipes.</p><p></p><p><strong>Determinant of Remaining Heat</strong></p><p>The glass is hot, so be careful not to touch it or put anything on it; doing so could cause damage.</p><p></p><p><strong>Timer with Built-In Stop Function</strong></p><p>Activates the active zone until the timer goes off.</p><p></p><p><strong>Control of Bridges</strong></p><p>If your induction cooktop (hob) has this capability, you can treat two adjacent zones as one and use a single command to control them both.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enhanced Capability</strong></p><p>Makes it possible to concentrate the entire induction burner's power on a specific area, allowing you to boil and cook food more quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Slide Management</strong></p><p>By simply gliding your finger from side to side, you can adjust the operating temperature, for instance, thanks to this convenient \\\"touch control\\\" system.</p><p></p><p><strong>Child Protection</strong></p><p>After you enable this feature, you can't use the controls to turn on the induction cooktop (hob).</p><p></p><p><strong>Protection from Overheating and Liquid Spills</strong></p><p>A safety feature will activate and turn off the stovetop (hob) in the event of an overheat or liquid spill.</p><p></p><hr/><p></p><p><strong>Oven Solutions</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Ovens: Massive Capacity and Peak Efficiency.</strong></p><p>With a 40-inch range that can hold up to 4 cubic feet of food, you'll have more than enough room for even the largest of dishes in any of our single or double combination ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>Electronic Temperature Control with Utmost Precision</strong></p><p>The oven's temperature stays consistent throughout thanks to the electronic control, unlike with traditional ovens.</p><p></p><p><strong>A 4.3-inch Full-Touch Screen</strong></p><p>The screen guarantees excellent legibility with TFT technology, showing every function with clear and immediate graphics.</p><p></p><p><strong>TFT Screen; Easy to Use, Extensive, and High-Resolution.</strong></p><p>Control all the functions of the single oven or both ovens with a single device: temperature, timer, and automatic cooking start and end programmer\\u2014all with one touch and at a glance\\u2014on the large display.</p><p></p><p><strong>Doors with a Gentle Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p>A shock absorber is integrated into the door hinges, allowing for a quieter and more gradual closing.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cabinet with Warming Drawer and Soft-Closing Mechanism</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>The Cooking Probe</strong></p><p>The tool you need to check the internal temperature of meat, among other things.</p><p></p><p><strong>Steam Ejection (Hot Food Preparation)</strong></p><p>You can achieve a crispy baked dish or a soft and juicy roast thanks to this system, which removes the vapors from inside the cavity, allowing you to choose a drier or more moist cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heat range: 85 to 575 degrees Fahrenheit</strong></p><p>You can effortlessly and perfectly prepare even the most intricate and sophisticated recipes in an ILVE oven, whether you're proofing, cooking, roasting, or using low heat.</p><p></p><p><strong>Using High Density Insulation and Tangential Cooling Ventilation</strong></p><p>Keeps the kitchen and its furniture from getting too hot.</p><p></p><p><strong>Effortless Cleaning with the Folding Grill Coil</strong></p><p>The electric heating element of the grill can be lowered for easier cleaning of the top part of the cavity, thanks to the articulated support.</p><p></p><p><strong>Dishwasher Safe Enamel</strong></p><p>Because the grease doesn't adhere to the surface, it's easier to clean.</p><p></p><p><strong>Essential Operations of the Oven. UOV 60 E3 TFT S</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Pizza party</li><li>Removing From Freeze</li><li>Cooking to extremes</li><li>A brief introduction</li><li>Extensive cooking with moisture</li><li>Grilling with a fan</li><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>Steaming food cooked in the air</li><li>Using the ground up</li><li>Cooking with moisture from below</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Static, moist, typical cooking</li><li>Using multiple fan cooking options</li><li>Several wet fan ovens</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Utility of Secondary Ovens. 30 E3 TFT UOV</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Grilling in a covered area</li><li>Aerial cuisine</li><li>An Underground Kitchen</li><li>Regular, static cooking</li><li>Sustainable cuisine</li></ul><hr/><p></p><p><strong>A Pizza Party</strong></p><p>Perfect for baking pizza, bread, and focaccia. The lower heating element is the primary heat source, and with the assistance of the other, less powerful heating elements, it produces the ideal conditions for this kind of cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Removing from Freeze</strong></p><p>Guarantees that any food that is frozen will defrost rapidly, bringing it to room temperature without changing its flavor or appearance.</p><p></p><p><strong>Extensive Preparation</strong></p><p>For foods that require a crispy finish, such as baked potatoes and veggies, chicken, salt-crusted fish, etc., this steam-discharge method guarantees rapid and intense cooking.</p><p></p><p><strong>Accelerated Boot</strong></p><p>Quick preheating gets the oven to the temperature you want it to be in no time at all, and then you can select the cooking mode that's going to work best with your food. When set to a low temperature, it can also defrost food quickly.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thoroughly Moist Cooking</strong></p><p>Its steam block ensures rapid and intense cooking and is ideal for moist foods such as braised meat, stewed rabbit, salt cod, and chicken cacciatore.</p><p></p><p><strong>Grilling with a Fan</strong></p><p>This function is great for a wide variety of foods because it is quick, deep, and uses a lot of energy. Some examples of these foods are sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, and pork chops.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enclosure for Grilling</strong></p><p>Functions such as quick and deep grilling, browning, roasting, and cooking fillets, Florentine steaks, fish, and vegetables are highly recommended.</p><p></p><p><strong>Cooking with Elevation</strong></p><p>This function is perfect for browning and finishing a wide variety of foods; burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc. all benefit from it.</p><p></p><p><strong>Elevated Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>Great for browning and giving a variety of foods that last splash of color a little more color without making them tough.</p><p></p><p><strong>Lessons in Home Cooking</strong></p><p>For pastries (biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, etc.), this is the best way to finish cooking the cycle.</p><p></p><p><strong>In-Depth Recipes for Moist Food</strong></p><p>If you want to finish the cooking cycle with the correct amount of moisture, this is the way to go.</p><p></p><p><strong>Standard, Static Cooking</strong></p><p>Electric ovens typically have this one setting that works well for things like roast veal, pork chops, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, meringues, biscuits, baked fruit, and more.</p><p></p><p><strong>Wet Static Regular Cooking</strong></p><p>Typical static cooking gets even more wet with this.</p><p></p><p><strong>Multi-Fan Oven Utilization</strong></p><p>You can bake a variety of foods at once without worrying about their aromas blending\\u2014lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc.\\u2014and save both time and energy thanks to this feature.</p><p></p><p><strong>A Variety of Moist Fan Recipes</strong></p><p>This increases the amount of moisture in a standard multi-fan oven.</p><p></p><p><strong>Sustainability in the Kitchen</strong></p><p>Slow roasting foods, like braised meats, white meats, baked pasta, and delicate pastries, necessitate longer cooking times when using the ECO function, which significantly reduces power consumption. However, this cooking cycle is not meant for foods that are frozen.</p><p></p><p><strong>Proposition 65 in California\\u2014</strong></p><p>Caution: Potential Cancer and Reproductive Risks</p><p><a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/.\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Visit www.P65Warnings.ca.gov for more information. C</a></p></div> <div><div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/qIZ8MSDCu-Y.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">Sorry, but the video tag isn't compatible with your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/RRQlYvQPAMg.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">The video tag is not supported by your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/Uh_EEzfUhUU.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;\\\">There is a problem with the video tag in your browser.</video> </div> <div> <video controls=\\\"\\\" preload=\\\"auto\\\" src=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/wKi6ZYNcCxY.mp4\\\" style=\\\"max-width:320px; margin-bo